Title: Scooby-Doo and the Cyber Chase
Genre: Animation, Action, Adventure, Comedy, Family, Mystery, Sci-Fi
Writer: Mark Turosz, William Hanna (based upon characters created by)
Actors: Scott Innes, Joe Alaskey, Bob Bergen, Grey Griffin
Plot: When Scooby and the gang get trapped in a video game created for them, they must fight against the 'Phantom Virus'. To escape the game they must go level by level and defeat the game once and for all.
